================================================================================
Change Log
================================================================================

##### Changes in libcfi version 1.1.0 (19jan15):

New and Changed Functionality:
- Removed the buggy compile-time check for NULL's value (CFI.h).
- Added V=1 command line option (Makefile).
- Changed INSTALL_INCLUDE and INSTALL_SHARE directories (Makefile).
- Added $(CROSS_COMPILE) for cross-building support (Makefile).
- Removed the RCS usage (Makefile).
- Removed the 'source' and 'objects' help targets (Makefile).
- Changed the handling of optimization and debug flags (Makefile).

Bugs Fixed:
- Fixed the definition of NULL (CFI.h).
- Fixed handling of 64-bit long symbols (io.c, string.c).

Things otherwise different:
- Fixed INSTALLPREFIX to be INSTALL_PREFIX (Makefile).
- Moved source into github and updated some documentation.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

