-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

##### Changes in libcfi version 0.50.0 (03may02):

	****************************************************************
	* There are many changes. The API is somewhat extended.        *
	****************************************************************

New Functionality:
- Memory allocated with new libcsc memory subsystem.
- Nodes and attributes atually deallocated.

Bugs Fixed:
- Memory leaks removed {memory now allocated with new libcsc memory subsystem}

Things otherwise different:
- None.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

##### Changes in libcfi version 0.35.0 (25jun00):

	****************************************************************
	* There are so many changes; I've even thrown away (archived)  *
	* the original revision history.  Consider this to be complete *
	* rebaseline.                                                  *
	****************************************************************

New Functionality:
- Strings are encoded/unencoded (ripped from libpropList).
- Attributes can be inserted/removed into/from word-attributes.
- cfi tree structure can be broken into several parts.
  o  each one can be written to its own file.
- Better control over I/O from/to files and stdout.

Bugs Fixed:
- Fixed (I think) trailing garbage occasionally occuring in attribute strings.

Things otherwise different:
- Too many: completely rebaselined.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

